@DATABASE "P-47"
@NODE "MAIN" "SPECCY POKES - P - P-47"
@TOC "MAIN"

                   ZX SPECTRUM (SPECCY heheh) POKES - P
                   ====================================

                                   P-47
                                   ====



DESCRIPTION              POKE
===========              ====

@{"Lives = x     " RXS "ADDRESS COMMAND ZXAMPoke(30252,254)"}          30252,x (x= 1-254)
@{"Speed = x     " rxs "address command zxampoke(30407,1) zxampoke(30799,1)"}          30407,x:30799,x
@{"Infinite Lives" rxs "address command zxampoke(30795,0)"}          30795,0


                         Change x to whatever value you wish, using
                         the POKE option on the ZXAM GUI. Simply
                         click the button to get the maximum value
                         x can be (usually 255).


                         This is one of my POKEs. Enjoy!

                         Rastan.
@endnode
